   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">
     <bold>
      <italic>S</italic>
      <sub>Chao1</sub>
     </bold>
    </td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">23</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">17</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">11</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">2</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
 <table-wrap-foot>
  <fn id="tb2fn1">
   <p>OTU, operational taxonomic unit.</p>
  </fn>
  <fn id="tb2fn2">
   <p>
    <italic>S</italic>
    <sub>Chao1</sub> represent the expected number of OTUs present in an environment if sampling were complete.
   </p>
  </fn>
  <fn id="tb2fn3">
   <p>Shannon's and Simpson's indices are measures of species diversity and both increase with increasing genetic diversity.</p>
  </fn>
 </table-wrap-foot>
</table-wrap>
